snippet.title: Earthbreakers Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Add Earthbreakers to your Steam wishlist!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1188870

Satellites rain death as factions fight for control of a Broken Earth. 
Protect your team's harvesters, build factories and vehicles, and assault the enemy base. 
Earthbreakers is team FPS action in an RTS world!

Join the discussion on Steam. Let us know what you think, and what you'd like to see included in the game
https://steamcommunity.com/app/1188870/discussions/
